strings.Value: "This a crazy road allll way to end, even crazier than how we meet... Now someone try steal OUR city? Nok-Nok say — we go steal it back!"
"It what heroes do. Walk together. Steal together. Stab together."
"You show more than how be hero — how be more true self. You teach Nok-Nok how to jester. Use head, but not as club — use to trick enemy. Turn laughter back to stab people."
"And you show me hero path, from goblin king, to great confronting of Munguk, to finding tribe again, and... uh, king-not-king again — hero path keep going. So do we."
"Pffft — Nok-Nok not let you go alone. Besides... be fun. Nok-Nok never stole a city back before."
"This a crazy road allll way to end, even crazier than how we meet... Now someone try steal city of Nok-Nok, King of Jesters? Nok-Nok say — we go jester thief to death!"
"Pffft — Nok-Nok not let you go alone. Besides... be fun. Nok-Nok never stole a city back before. Be tale of Jester greater than any Hero!"
"Nok-Nok never had to be hero — you showed Nok-Nok only had to be Nok-Nok. Jester. Not someone else."

"All way from goblin king, to great confronting of Munguk, to finding tribe again, and... uh, king-not-king again — all led to being Jester. But need city back first, or Jester have no place to jester."
